2017年4月3日，[[聖彼得堡地鐵|聖彼得堡地鐵]][[干草广场站|干草广场站]]到[[科技学院站|科技学院站]]间发生爆炸，共造成14人死亡<ref name="MacFarquhar">{{cite web|last1=MacFarquhar|first1=Neil|last2=Nechepureneko|first2=Ivan|title=Explosion in St. Petersburg Metro Kills at Least 10|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/03/world/europe/st-petersburg-russia-explosion.html?_r=0|website=nytimes.com|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2017-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170406225703/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/03/world/europe/st-petersburg-russia-explosion.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-39478165|title=Взрыв в метро Санкт-Петербурга: погибли 10 человек|last=|first=|date=2017-04-03|work=BBC Russia|language=ru|trans_title=Explosion in Metro St. Petersburg, killing 10 people|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613155343/https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-39478165|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=RIA1>{{Cite news |url=https://ria.ru/incidents/20170403/1491389397.html?utm_source=push&utm_medium=browser_notification&utm_campaign=ria.ru |title=В петербургской больнице скончались двое пострадавших при взрыве в метро |work=ria.ru |trans_title=Two injured in the explosion in the subway died in the St. Petersburg hospital |access-date=2017-04-03 |language=ru |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618175454/https://ria.ru/incidents/20170403/1491389397.html?utm_source=push&utm_medium=browser_notification&utm_campaign=ria.ru |dead-url=no }}</ref>，另外至少有45人受伤。爆炸装备装在公文包中<ref name="BBC2">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-39481770 |title=St Petersburg metro explosions kill ten - media |publisher=BBC |date=2017-04-03 |accessdate=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2017-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407174932/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-39481770 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Reuters1">{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-russia-metro-blast-idUSKBN1751A6 |title=At least 10 people may have been killed by Russia metro blast: TASS |publisher=Reuters |date=2017-04-03 |accessdate=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123140348/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-russia-metro-blast-idUSKBN1751A6 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RT1">{{cite web |url=https://www.rt.com/news/383202-st-petersburg-blast-metro/ |title=Explosion in St. Petersburg Metro, fatalities confirmed (GRAPHIC IMAGES) |publisher=Russia Today |date=2017-04-03 |accessdate=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2017-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409002333/https://www.rt.com/news/383202-st-petersburg-blast-metro/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第二枚爆炸装置在[[起义广场站|起义广场站]]的列车中寻获，並已拆除<ref name="BBC1" />。

==袭击==
2017年4月3日，一枚装有重约1公斤的爆炸物的装置在一辆列车途径[[干草广场站|干草广场站]]到[[科技学院站|科技学院站]]之间隧道时引爆<ref name="BBC2" /><ref name="rbcfeed">{{cite news |title=В Санкт-Петербурге произошел взрыв в метро. Онлайн-трансляция |trans-title=In St. Petersburg, there was an explosion in the Metro |url=http://www.rbc.ru/textonlines/03/04/2017/58e238789a7947f42e875f91 |accessdate=2017-04-03 |work=RBC |language=ru |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618210443/https://www.rbc.ru/textonlines/03/04/2017/58e238789a7947f42e875f91 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Jansen">{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2017/04/03/subway-security-st-petersburg-new-york-london-paris-brussels/99988934/|title=Russian subway bombing reveals terror vulnerability|last=Jansen|first=Bart|date=2017-04-03|work=USA Today|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124085759/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2017/04/03/subway-security-st-petersburg-new-york-london-paris-brussels/99988934/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。爆炸消息传出后，圣彼得堡所有地铁站立即关闭<ref name="BBC2"/><ref name="RT1"/>。至深夜，地铁3、4、5号线的恢复运营<ref name="BBC2"/><ref name="RT1"/>。

据[[国际文传电讯社|国际文传电讯社]]报道，事件疑似由一名[[中亚|中亚]]的{{le|伊斯兰极端主义|Islamic extremism}}自杀式袭击者策划<ref>{{cite web|title=St Petersburg metro explosion: Anti-terror police hunting suspects|url=http://www.news.com.au/world/europe/st-petersburg-reportedly-rocked-by-explosion-on-train-causing-injuries/news-story/90db1a31cf16a2d0e79c14d3e301ac6c|website=News.com.au|accessdate=2017-04-04|date=2017-04-04|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808194837/http://www.news.com.au/world/europe/st-petersburg-reportedly-rocked-by-explosion-on-train-causing-injuries/news-story/90db1a31cf16a2d0e79c14d3e301ac6c|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-39486640|title=St Petersburg metro explosion suspect 'from Central Asia'|publisher=BBC News|date=2017-04-03|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020403/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-39486640|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="mknames">{{cite news|url=http://www.mk.ru/incident/2017/04/04/predpolagaemyy-terroristsmertnik-opoznan-v-sanktperetburge.html|language=ru|trans-title=Alleged suicide bomber in St. Petersburg identified|title=Названо имя предполагаемого террориста-смертника в Санкт-Петербурге|date=2017-04-04|work=Moskovskij Komsomolets|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2020-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909050654/https://www.mk.ru/incident/2017/04/04/predpolagaemyy-terroristsmertnik-opoznan-v-sanktperetburge.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Telegraph/>。

第二枚爆炸装置在[[起义广场站|起义广场站]]的列车中寻获，随后被拆除<ref name=Metro1>{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/04/03/multiple-injuries-after-huge-explosion-rocks-st-petersburg-metro-6550828/ |title=At least ten dead after huge ‘nail bomb’ explosion on St Petersburg metro |first=Toby |last=Meyjes |publisher=Associated Newspapers Ltd |work=Metro |accessdate=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025233751/https://metro.co.uk/2017/04/03/multiple-injuries-after-huge-explosion-rocks-st-petersburg-metro-6550828/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据报装备采用[[滚珠轴承|滚珠轴承]]、螺丝和[[破片杀伤|碎片]]<ref name=TG>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/04/03/saintpetersburg-bombing-casualties-explosion-metro-train/ |title=St Petersburg Metro explosion: CCTV image of suspect emerges after at least 10 killed by 'briefcase' bomb |date=2017-04-03 |website=Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group |access-date=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2017-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408101345/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/04/03/saintpetersburg-bombing-casualties-explosion-metro-train/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，藏匿于灭火器中，装有一公斤TNT<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lister|first1=Tim|last2=Burrows|first2=Emily|last3=Dewan|first3=Angela|title=St. Petersburg metro explosion: At least 10 dead in Russia blast|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/04/03/europe/st-petersburg-russia-explosion/index.html|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902005005/https://www.cnn.com/2017/04/03/europe/st-petersburg-russia-explosion/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==事後==
事发后安保升级，金属探测器重新投入使用。[[2010年莫斯科地铁连环爆炸事件|七年前曾发生连环爆炸袭击]]的[[莫斯科地铁|莫斯科地铁]]亦加强戒备，谨防袭击再次发生风险。莫斯科表示准备好协助圣彼得堡地铁。当地媒体报道称警方还在三个莫斯科地铁车站中找到可疑包裹，并疏散地区<ref name="AL">{{citeweb|title=Взрыв в метро Санкт-Петербурга: онлайн-трансляция|url=http://www.mk.ru/incident/2017/04/03/vzryv-v-metro-sanktpeterburga-onlayntranslchciya.html|publisher=MK|accessdate=2017-04-04|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409112639/http://www.mk.ru/incident/2017/04/03/vzryv-v-metro-sanktpeterburga-onlayntranslchciya.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据未经证实的报道，地铁监控摄像头曾拍到疑犯<ref name="BBC1" />。[[俄罗斯联邦侦查委员会|俄罗斯联邦侦查委员会]]表示事发时列车司机决定不刹停列车，避免造成更大的伤亡<ref name="BBC1" />。

目前尚无负责袭击的声明<ref name=DW>{{cite web |url=http://www.dw.com/en/st-petersburg-metro-hit-by-deadly-blast/a-38270321 |title=St. Petersburg metro hit by deadly blast |date=2017-04-03 |publisher=Deutsche Welle |access-date=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2017-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408174306/http://www.dw.com/en/st-petersburg-metro-hit-by-deadly-blast/a-38270321 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。联邦侦查委员会将事件定性为“恐怖袭击”<ref name=ECON>{{cite web |url=https://rueconomics.ru/237932-vzryv-v-metro-peterburga-oficialno-priznan-teraktom |title=Взрыв в метро Петербурга официально признан терактом [Explosion in the Petersburg's metro officially recognised as a terrorist attack.] |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2017-04-03 |website=Экономика сегодня |publisher=ФБА «Экономика сегодня» |accessdate=2017-04-03 |language=ru |archive-date=2017-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404130451/https://rueconomics.ru/237932-vzryv-v-metro-peterburga-oficialno-priznan-teraktom |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。袭击据信是[[自杀袭击|自杀式炸弹袭击]]。

